# Master Specification: Automation-Infinite (Sovereign AGI)

This document serves as the high-fidelity blueprint for **Automation-Infinite**, a self-scaling Personal AGI (Sovereign Tier) designed for **Pashin Kasad**. It integrates the knowledge-base of the [[Second-Brain]] with the agentic motors of [[Automation5]] and [[Office-Intelligence]] into a recursive, self-improving ecosystem.

---

## 💎 1. Philosophical Foundation: The Sovereign AGI
The system is built on the **[[Personal-Philosophy|Builder-Founder DNA]]** and follows the **[[Nerd-Culture-Psychology|Limit-Breaking]]** mental models. It does not just automate tasks; it acts with **Agency**—it identifies vacuums in the user's world and fills them autonomously.

