## 🧪 5. Verification & Safety Protocols
- **Git Sandboxing**: 100% of autonomous code must live on a `sentinel-` branch before being merged.
- **Archetype Validation**: The AGI must justify its persona selection in `logs/persona_audit.log`.
- **Budget Sentinel**: Kill-switch triggered if any projected cost exceeds the current Spend-Valve Level.
